messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content: I finally got an alfredo sauce pizza. Worth it.

messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content: So I found this really cool looking rock. I might keep it.

messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content: I should know to RUN when Newt has a pillow equipped.

messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content: Y'all. It SNEW. I just about froze my tail off out there. Good thing nothing is sticking to the ground.

messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content:
Just a thing I learned about myself:
If there's a thing I want that doesn't exist, I got ways to make it happen!

messages.author: Ashley Hunter
messages.content:
I need to learn how to make something special for the people in my life.
If only I had enough crafting skill.....
